001package com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.types;
002
003import android.os.Build;
004
005import androidx.annotation.Nullable;
006
007@SuppressWarnings("unused")
008public class WalletMetadata {
009
010    private final String osType;
011    private final String manufacturer;
012    private String pushToken;
013    private final String appPackage;
014    private final String sdkVersion;
015    private final String osVersion;
016    private final String model;
017
018    public WalletMetadata(String appPackage, String pushToken) {
019        this.osType = "ANDROID";
020        this.manufacturer = Build.MANUFACTURER;
021        this.pushToken = pushToken;
022        this.appPackage = appPackage;
023        this.sdkVersion = String.valueOf(Build.VERSION.SDK_INT);
024        this.osVersion = Build.VERSION.RELEASE;
025        this.model = Build.MODEL;
026    }
027
028    public void setPushToken(String pushToken) {
029        this.pushToken = pushToken;
030    }
031
032    public String getOsType() {
033        return osType;
034    }
035
036    public String getManufacturer() {
037        return manufacturer;
038    }
039
040    public String getPushToken() {
041        return pushToken;
042    }
043
044    public String getAppPackage() {
045        return appPackage;
046    }
047
048    public String getSdkVersion() {
049        return sdkVersion;
050    }
051
052    public String getOsVersion() {
053        return osVersion;
054    }
055
056    public String getModel() {
057        return model;
058    }
059}
